{"tid":400702,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有無咩 自動上鏈錶盒 好介紹","createTime":"2017-09-15T04:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T10:12:48.000Z","uid":82494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"00b7bfaa0cee79705ac8d7fd84e982955392efaf","tid":400702,"uid":82494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T04:41:25.000Z","msg":"最近老豆送左隻自動錶當生日禮物比我 普通Tissot  <br />\n<br />\n但因為我訓覺唔慣帶手錶 <br />\n<br />\n所以除低左 今朝起身見停左 <br />\n<br />\n但又唔想次次帶親都上鏈 重較時間 好麻煩 <br />\n<br />\n所以想問下大家有無搖錶器好介紹 唔使太貴 <br />\n<br />\n唔該哂大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef628f16747643bd3c80e14b94f84669550e96e","tid":400702,"uid":82494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T06:04:35.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"5f8204903bdee7f2c0237c7745fdecb4ff409096","tid":400702,"uid":83569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T06:43:48.000Z","msg":"我反而想知有冇靚既純粹錶盒介紹 想用黎放遺物手錶好耐..."},{"pid":"234b37b37b76b59bffceea6bd2f48bfe601438ab","tid":400702,"uid":66501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T06:55:41.000Z","msg":"淘寶2~300\t蚊都有"},{"pid":"0600c0d9ddf5cc3443006d3dc009f33c273a652e","tid":400702,"uid":82494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:34:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淘寶2~300\t蚊都有</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好唔好用? 會唔會整爆隻錶?"},{"pid":"a180008119458d294b2ce77cfbed9dadfd822af2","tid":400702,"uid":33338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:40:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>淘寶2~300\t蚊都有</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好唔好用? 會唔會整爆隻錶?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n入電池果啲爆都唔會整爆隻錶啦 <br />\n利申 用左成年"},{"pid":"7fcb3288a74240182ff8a37bb924566f2474e59e","tid":400702,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:42:41.000Z","msg":"有得佢停比較好"},{"pid":"01b6968ead0901bf03f4957bca50849e45576f37","tid":400702,"uid":82494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T13:01:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有得佢停比較好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但睇文話長時間唔郁 入面d油會乾 無咁好 係咪嫁？？"},{"pid":"06a4db263cc521fa24af61311c00c702d7bbc6e4","tid":400702,"uid":82494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T13:05:00.000Z","msg":"其實，無論是自動機械錶，還是手動機械錶。如果你長時間不佩戴並停止轉動。會加快機油和潤滑劑的老化速度，從而提高手錶的使用壽命和節約保養費用。畢竟零件老化的維修相當麻煩。所以一般錶迷請持續為其上鏈。這樣可以減慢老化速度。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？"},{"pid":"a93760fdccd6e3bedec7eeca18896f1044f4626f","tid":400702,"uid":101201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T13:10:55.000Z","msg":"淘寶   用左三個月   乜事都無   兩舊幾水"},{"pid":"b9d5f18cff411f279aad0cbd8af14f2d5d282e6c","tid":400702,"uid":4181,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T00:47:49.000Z","msg":"咁垃圾,一個夜晚就停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n手動上鏈,唔洗拉錶的,就咁向上扭"},{"pid":"3aad95455b79a1ba779ef3c4a2f07456f4634002","tid":400702,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T01:11:01.000Z","msg":"用緊淘寶，質量麻麻，不過都係要佢轉姐港紙2xx<br />\n<br />\n真係有人會訓教戴錶?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f1eb49694de8b9bc95395e2e7eea0bc03ff811","tid":400702,"uid":36100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T01:29:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用緊淘寶，質量麻麻，不過都係要佢轉姐港紙2xx<br />\n<br />\n真係有人會訓教戴錶?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗瞓覺會戴錶嘅人唔多<br />\n但係一晚就停嘅錶會少啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪隻錶有咩問題？"},{"pid":"4c227d6a4a44f8a1fb3952a9d05cd9f4622221c1","tid":400702,"uid":36100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T01:30:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用緊淘寶，質量麻麻，不過都係要佢轉姐港紙2xx<br />\n<br />\n真係有人會訓教戴錶?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗瞓覺會戴錶嘅人唔多<br />\n但係一晚就停嘅錶會少啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><